Body: What We've Learned Updated: The customer wants to run the FileSystemOverview report in AIC but was getting an error message: Arithmetic overflow error converting expression to data type int. Team on SWAT suggested running FS_Schema instant job. However, after running that job customer is getting errors in FSAA Bulk Import and FSA_Schema job too. These errors refer some DB tables that are not present.
Next Steps Updated: Dev team has asked for an escalation. However, prior to that, list of DB tables is required so that issue can be sorted out at earliest.

@Pasan Illege​ thanks for tagging this ticket as "KB needed". This error message is definitely something we want to highlight in the KB. Could you flesh out your resolution notes to confirm the exact error message and root cause, and why the Create Schema job resolves the data type conversion issue? Then @Nicholas Zimmer​ and I can turn it into an article. Thank you!
